data.description: Rare opportunity in this 5BR/4BA home next to Raspberry Ridge Park & walkable to Jeffers Pond Elementary. Basketball, volleyball & jungle gym steps from your back door. Step from entry foyer w/ coat closet into open-concept gathering room/dining/kitchen area w/ granite, SS appliances & door to deck overlooking fully fenced backyard. From kitchen, keep an eye on the kids as they play in the family room w/ cozy gas burning FP. Adjacent formal dining leads to formal living at front of the house. 1/2 bath for guests & mud room/laundry connect to large 3-car garage - perfect for workout space/hobbies/3rd vehicle. Four bedrooms on 2nd level & spacious shared 2nd floor full bath. King-size primary w/ sitting area, walk-in closet & ensuite bath w/ separate jetted tub & shower. Spacious family room in LL has 2nd fireplace & walk-out slider to backyard. 5th BR, Craft/flex room, 3/4 bath & large storage/utility space round out the LL. Home is mins to parks, shops, restaurants, & schools.
